<% title 'What is required' %>
<% step_header(path: '/entrypoint/v1') %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl">Before you continue</span>
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">What you’ll need to complete your application</h1>

    <p class="govuk-body">You will need the following:</p>

    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>details of the other people (the respondents), including their date of birth</li>
      <li>contact details of the respondents, including their current address</li>
      <li>solicitor details (if you have asked one to represent you)</li>
      <li>details of any previous family court cases</li>
      <li>signed document confirming <abbr title="Mediation Information and Assessment Meeting">MIAM</abbr> attendance
        (if applicable)
      </li>
      <li>
        completed and signed
        <%= link_to(
          'certificate of suitability',
          'https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/form-fp9-certificate-of-suitability-of-litigation-friend',
          class: 'govuk-link',
          target: :_blank,
          rel: :external
          )
        %> or copy of the court order appointing a ‘litigation friend’ if any of the people making this application are under 18
      </li>
      <li>the child’s or children’s details, including date of birth</li>
      <li>email account if you want confirmation when your application has been submitted electronically, or a printer
        if you’d prefer to send by post
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="govuk-inset-text">
      If you do not know all of the details you can still complete your application but it will take longer to process.
    </div>

    <%= link_to 'Continue', entrypoint_how_long_path, class: 'govuk-button govuk-!-margin-top-3', role: 'button', draggable: false, data: { module: 'govuk-button' } %>
  </div>
</div>
